{"tid":2294672,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"逆權電影《佔領立法會》明爭金馬最佳紀錄片 陳果《墮胎師》衝導演獎：弱勢勝算高","createTime":"2020-11-21T08:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T15:13:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"27366fcd3d4a5a767fb8a437228ad699ffa25ab9","tid":2294672,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:00:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201120/FMWITSZZNFFIBGWLHHROWRVNZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201120%2FFMWITSZZNFFIBGWLHHROWRVNZM%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM302FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=da39b695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201120%2FFMWITSZZNFFIBGWLHHROWRVNZM%2F&h=805d45c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201120/FMWITSZZNFFIBGWLHHROWRVNZM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n陳果《墮胎師》衝導演獎：弱勢勝算高 <br />\n逆權電影《佔領立法會》明爭金馬最佳紀錄片<br />\n<br />\n【第57屆金馬獎】【《蘋果》專訪】台灣第57屆金馬獎頒獎典禮明晚在台北國父紀念館舉行，今屆共有七齣港片入圍多個獎項（詳見附表），當中最受注目的是講述去年7月1日逆權人士進入香港立法會三小時的《佔領立法會》，入圍最佳紀錄片。憑《墮胎師》爭最佳導演的陳果早前接受《蘋果》專訪，覺得弱勢電影反而勝算更高。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：桂綸鎂潑婦上身搶影后<br />\n<br />\n台灣第57屆金馬獎將於明晚揭盅，今屆最受關注的是兩部香港逆權紀錄片《佔領立法會》及《迷航》入圍最佳紀錄片，反映大會對香港爭取民主的重視，而且今次是繼2009年張經緯的港產紀錄片《音樂人生》，於金馬獎獲得最佳紀錄片、最佳音效、最佳剪輯三獎後再次揚威。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/807AqMeTVe4VRpYv2bqj6M9uaZU=/640x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FTO7AC7MBJGF5AVXNJTANQQLIY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F807AqMeTVe4VRpYv2bqj6M9uaZU%3D%2F640x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFTO7AC7MBJGF5AVXNJTANQQLIY.jpg&h=76a838e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳果憑《墮胎師》再次入圍金馬獎最佳導演，他受訪時表示台灣金馬獎評審較客觀，只要好睇就有機會獲獎。攝影：沈健程<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2tPQ9EHoNe-4MpX31c-blF4O080=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3EZICHBBLVH53FM2MAPA7PHUZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2tPQ9EHoNe-4MpX31c-blF4O080%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3EZICHBBLVH53FM2MAPA7PHUZQ.jpg&h=905ab7da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■逆權紀錄片《佔領立法會》紀錄了去年7月1日抗爭者進入立法會的歷史一幕。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CRnfwD2s7ud7gclfrDBRjSa0El8=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YLFC4USK3ZBJRAIVHZJAWAURPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCRnfwD2s7ud7gclfrDBRjSa0El8%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYLFC4USK3ZBJRAIVHZJAWAURPI.jpg&h=6f022f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■短片《夜更》於去年底逆權運動期間拍攝，有大量真實抗爭場面。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UJYXrjkCO_j9Sj7P7mCCmVWLDUY=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FPBRC5HJKFAHVESMJAAJ7Z2UUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUJYXrjkCO_j9Sj7P7mCCmVWLDUY%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFPBRC5HJKFAHVESMJAAJ7Z2UUA.jpg&h=e35c809a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《迷航》紀錄了2011年內地烏坎村村民集體抗爭事件。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n導演撐抗爭匿名避打壓<br />\n<br />\n兩部逆權片均紀錄大量抗爭場面，《佔領立法會》由多位紀錄片工作者匿名執導，紀錄去年7月1日香港「立法會被佔領」事件，被視為極珍貴的香港史片段。可是，該片遭打壓未能在本港主流戲院上映，只能以「打游擊」方式在灣仔古天樂影院放映，但每次戲飛開售都火速售罄。而《迷航》則由香港女導演李哲昕執導，紀錄2011年內地烏坎村村民集體抗爭貪官非法變賣土地，村民選出抗爭領袖執掌村委會事件。該片於去年剪輯成最後版本，入選過溫哥華影展、香港亞洲電影節及台灣國際紀錄片影展亞洲視野競賽。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：劉俊謙、霍嘉豪香港新勢力<br />\n<br />\n另外，曾執導電影《十年．浮瓜》的導演郭臻的短片《夜更》則入圍最佳劇情短片。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pHzxDgNJL8Gc1rW5jr1yzUKjfHc=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N6TRK222SRF5FJP3KR36BTF7YQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpHzxDgNJL8Gc1rW5jr1yzUKjfHc%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN6TRK222SRF5FJP3KR36BTF7YQ.jpg&h=e0c6d866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■白靈（左）憑陳果執導的《墮胎師》入圍最佳女主角。劇照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/weFgA06YbHq9qhafJDzI_sIIqLM=/950x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AOJLBJGNH5GLZGS23U67DZLQNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FweFgA06YbHq9qhafJDzI_sIIqLM%3D%2F950x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAOJLBJGNH5GLZGS23U67DZLQNU.jpg&h=ebe5fc58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■蔡明亮（小圖）今年憑同志電影《日子》，第八度入圍金馬最佳導演。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指金像可「班馬」投票<br />\n<br />\n另外，現年61歲的陳果憑執導《墮胎師》再次入圍金馬最佳導演，日前他接受《蘋果》專訪，提到23年前憑《香港製造》贏得金馬最佳導演，同年參賽港片有陳可辛《甜蜜蜜》及王家衛《春光乍洩》。陳果指當年《香港製造》算是弱勢，陳可辛和王家衛的作品是強勢大片，他說︰「金馬獎有少少歐洲電影節味道，唔係純商業，當然商業拍得好都會攞。」他表示《甜蜜蜜》雖然是主流片，但講的都是人民關懷，結構如早兩年的《淪落人》︰「評審嚟講金馬真係搵好多人嚟評，香港行荷李活嗰套，你可以班馬搵人填夠咪得囉，大包圍票多就贏。喺台灣細片反而有機會，評審經過一輪討論去判獎，唔似香港嗰種較工業。」他說不少老牌香港導演都傾向合拍片，而近年湧現的年輕導演傾向社會議題電影，令非主流電影在金像獎中多了獲獎機會。<br />\n<br />\n其實，自。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：何永寧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/B4cDNORGev0Eujo6by-tooV55n4=/495x1412/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VHJ4JLGQ7RD3PJUISYJWDRSIAY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FB4cDNORGev0Eujo6by-tooV55n4%3D%2F495x1412%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVHJ4JLGQ7RD3PJUISYJWDRSIAY.gif&h=bcd565b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acdf6305c7037dd13efb5cd3aaba30db1c8be4d4","tid":2294672,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:02:41.000Z","msg":"今日"},{"pid":"331c20a7396741d0ca9db600ffa2e2f2f19cda39","tid":2294672,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:03:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19e495d612fae9601305aa7ec071b6b14dd4d80a","tid":2294672,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:04:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bc7f6bd11c29e2de318ba2ed2aaeb0f39f55d3b","tid":2294672,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:04:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea6c03369194ddd5f81f9819f79e61a18cc35876","tid":2294672,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c1e8cf5906e1821e6b358abf67b534474013aa9","tid":2294672,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:07:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72d3bd122dbfbf7321622a3db7c296698029e2c6","tid":2294672,"uid":166729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"最緊要手捲煙收皮, 垃圾片唔上映, 扮晒野"},{"pid":"e68a28ec5cde05be78b67891972be03cc68f2f9f","tid":2294672,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:16:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2cabb88ae060de72b8e1561e81873c5c0350346","tid":2294672,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ac70e3f3512efd289618090747f2ac90cd14da7","tid":2294672,"uid":166729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e68a28ec5cde05be78b67891972be03cc68f2f9f","tid":2294672,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72d3bd122dbfbf7321622a3db7c296698029e2c6","tid":2294672,"uid":166729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:11:07.000Z","msg":"最緊要手捲煙收皮, 垃圾片唔上映, 扮晒野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:16:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"睇劇情簡介應該係垃圾<br />\n又唔上映又扮晒勁咁, 有咩資格攞獎"},{"pid":"d629f579de8f7c39c88b31705747bd98500363c7","tid":2294672,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:51:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6123c1afbfde5686cea38c75a29f1d93669c36f","tid":2294672,"uid":286921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T13:58:26.000Z","msg":"《墮胎師》點解可以零宣傳<br />\n<br />\nBtw 百靈 like 過手足comment⋯ 雖然嗰排好似咩fans留言都like <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337c916df7c2bff6eebd1adc6519a90204ddbab8","tid":2294672,"uid":15213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d629f579de8f7c39c88b31705747bd98500363c7","tid":2294672,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ac70e3f3512efd289618090747f2ac90cd14da7","tid":2294672,"uid":166729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e68a28ec5cde05be78b67891972be03cc68f2f9f","tid":2294672,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:16:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"睇劇情簡介應該係垃圾<br />\n又唔上映又扮晒勁咁, 有咩資格攞獎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T08:51:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"呢條友不停狙擊套戲<br />\n套戲剛剛先在影展首映<br />\n乜宣傳都未有<br />\n咁快上係花式自殺<br />\n<br />\n仲要冇睇過套戲"}]}